	<summary>Sitecore Helix library that adds new Fields to Sitecore.</summary>
	<description>
Verndale Helix Catalog is a collection of utilities for the Sitecore .NET CMS.
The Foundation.Fields library introduces a few new field types to Sitecore.

New Field: Custom Repeat Field
This field derives from the concept of the name/value list field, with the following enhancements:
a. Authors can "Group" values.
b. Authors can create values based on more than just single-line text. Current support includes RTE, General Link, Multilist, etc.


Installation
1. Add this NuGet package to your Sitecore solution
2. Build and Deploy your solution to a target environment

This library requires the installation of a Sitecore package (included). this should happen automatically when you build and deploy
your project.


Configured for use with Sitecore 9.0.
Requires Sitecore 9.0 NuGet packages, available here: https://sitecore.myget.org/F/sc-packages/api/v3/index.json
Requires the installation of the included Package.
